    "title": "Junior Investment Banker at Yes Bank Global Group",
    "description": "Grow your career with Yes Bank Global Group! We are hiring a Investment Banker for our Delhi team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Yes Bank Global Group:\nYes Bank Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in VBA\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Yes Bank Global Group!",
